---
layout: post
title: "<em>isTRUE</em>: check if exactly TRUE and length 1"
date: 2017-08-26
category: R_function
tags: [R, function, logic]
---

```
x <- TRUE
isTRUE(x)
# [1] TRUE

y <- c(TRUE, TRUE)
isTRUE(y) 
# [1] FALSE

x <- c("hello")
isTRUE(x) 
# [1] FALSE

x <- c(1)
isTRUE(x) 
# [1] FALSE

isTRUE(1) 
# [1] FALSE
```

<small> viewed on http://www.rfunction.com </small>

